<P>
 How big a story is Germany's quarterfinal loss to Bulgaria Sunday? 
</P>
<P>
 A reporter from the German newspaper Bild was asked: 
</P>
<P>
 Is this bigger than Boris Becker winning Wimbledon? 
</P>
<P>
 "Yes," he said. 
</P>
<P>
 Is this bigger than Becker and Steffi Graf winning at Wimbledon in the same 
year? 
</P>
<P>
 "Yes," he said. 
</P>
<P>
 Well, just how big is it? 
</P>
<P>
 "The biggest," he said. 
</P>
<P>
 German defender Thomas Strunz was asked what he expected upon the team's 
return home. 
</P>
<P>
