<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA071194-0041 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 059503 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 11, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 5; Column 1; View Desk 
