 Wrong captions-Photo captions of Taconic Resources executive Richard Chase and 
consultant James Jevens were mistakenly reversed Sunday in a report on the 
Weldon Canyon ballot measure in the West County Edition of The Times. The two 
men are accurately identified in photos above. 
</P>
